high_descs: Turn around and walk left to the left side of the toilet.
Take the towel off the towel rack on the wall.
Place the towel on the toilet tank in the front left corner.
anns.task_desc: Place a towel on a toilet tank.

high_descs: Turn around and go left to face the towel hanging to the right of the mirror.
Take the towel down from the towel ring.
Turn to the right to face the toilet.
Put the towel on the back of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Put a towel on the back of a toilet.

high_descs: Turn around, walk to the walk, then turn left and walk to the sink.
Remove the towel from the hanger.
Turn to the left, then to the left, then turn around to face the toilet.
Place the towel on the toilet tank.
anns.task_desc: Move the towel from the hanger to the back of the toilet.
